EN: The company decided to cut costs.
ZH: 由于市场需求下降，他们不得不缩减生产。
EN: Due to a decrease in market demand, they had to reduce production.
ZH: 我们需要缩减总部的工作人员数量。
EN: We need to reduce the number of employees at the headquarters.
ZH: 为了降低开支，他们正在考虑缩减旅行费用。
EN: To cut expenses, they are considering reducing travel costs.
ZH: 他们计划缩减部门的规模以提高效率。
EN: They plan to downsize the department to improve efficiency.
ZH: 这家企业将缩减生产线，以适应市场需求。
EN: This company will streamline production lines to meet market demand.
ZH: 老板面临困难的时候，不得不缩减工资。
EN: When the boss faced difficulties, he had to cut salaries.
